    {
      "note": "Summary of Original Version",
      "abstract": "Amend KRS 141.010 to define \"qualified tips\" and \"qualified overtime compensation\"; amend KRS 141.019 to allow the same treatment of qualified tips in accordance with 26 U.S.C. sec. 224 and qualified overtime compensation in accordance with 26 U.S.C. sec. 225; RETROACTIVE; EMERGENCY."
    }
